  Rule: 9 consecutive days with 0c and empty hold (no gold, no goods) → remove or rookie; rookie only if home had dock wholesale this day, commerce pulse ≥0.20, or ≥36 tradeable units in stock (excl. gold/silver). dock: fire-sale to officer purse (ships×1c) if short, then dust-sell up to 8u while purse below base 28c + neuroticism bump. Start 78–295c. Bankruptcy rookies: chance 0.46 to charter cheapest slip hull at home (listing removed, condition from listing, port wealth −ask/14). NPC peer loans: docked merchants may borrow coin (max 2 debts); sell margin repays creditors; traits bias avoiding creditors' home ports and fleeing shared docks.
